00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:16,820
This is Company Commander Kim's CT scan.

369
00:28:16,820 --> 00:28:20,590
You see this small dot here, right? It's shrapnel from a landmine.

370
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:24,880
One, two, three, four, five, six.

371
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:27,170
